            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="23005030">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23005030/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p23005030-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class=""> 历史无法假设，谁又会知道如何呢</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23005030/">(<span class="">12回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-12-07 16:05</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">3人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p23005030-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>历史无法假设，谁又会知道如何呢
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
